				"synopsis": {
					"type": 23,
					"value": "One of four messenger rats being trained in Jaheira's basement. The rats themselves are there for flavour and need to remain a single voiceline only each, but could do with conveying why Jaheira has multiple rats and a badger in her basement - IE for delivering messages around Baldur's Gate."
